high_descs: Turn around and move to the small desk on the left side of the bookshelf.
Pick up the black pen on the desk between the two yellow pencils.
Turn to your right and go to the desk at the end of the room.
Open the top drawer and place the pen inside and close it.
Find the pen next to the clock on top of the desk.
Pick up the pen off the top of the desk.
Find the drawer where you place the other pen in the desk.
Open the top drawer and place the pen inside and close it.
anns.task_desc: Get the black pens and place in the top drawer of the desk.

high_descs: Go to the desk to your left, with the lamp on it.
Pick up the pen on the desk, behind the clock.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go to the wall, then turn left to face the desk.
Open the top drawer of the desk, put the pen inside, and close it.
Look up to the top of the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk.
Move back down to the top drawer of the desk.
Open the top drawer of the desk, put the pen inside, and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens in the top drawer of the desk.

high_descs: Turn around to your right face the desk
Pick up the pen on the desk
Turn right then head desk with drawers
Open the drawer put the pen inside then close it
Move closer to the desk
Pick up the pen on the desk beside the bowl
Turn to your left then move backwards
Open the drawer then put in the pen then close it
anns.task_desc: Put the two pen in the desk drawer
